\pard\keepn \plain\b\fs28 Charm Spells\plain\fs24 
\par \pard 
\par \fs20 The pride of the Mages guild, these types of spells have the ability of controlling certain types of creatures ranging from Humanoids to Dragons and causing them to befriend the spellcaster, becoming their companion.  It is said that none can resist a Mage who has mastered this class of magical spells.  The effectiveness of these spells depends on the casters experience and the Magic and Charm Resistance of the monster.
\par \fs24 
