\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 1\tab Guilds: Mag
\par Required Stats: 12 Int, 12 Wis\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 4 Monsters in 1 Group to be Charmed.\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 This spell will bind one or more insects to the caster, causing them to become companions.
\par 
\par \b Charm Animal\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 2\tab Guilds: Mag
\par Required Stats: 12 Int, 12 Wis, 14 Cha\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 4 Monsters in 1 Group to be Charmed.\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 An excellent spell for charming vicious animals, causing them to befriend the caster.
\par \pard\li175 
\par \b Charm Elemental\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 3\tab Guilds: Mag
\par Required Stats: 13 Int, 13 Wis, 15 Cha\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 4 Monsters in 1 Group to be Charmed.\tab 
