\pard\keepn \plain\b\fs28 Element Spells\plain\fs24 
\par \pard 
\par \fs20 In the Sorcerer\'92s continued study of destruction, which included the study of Acid, Disease and Poisons, birthed spells of the Element type.  Deadly in nature, these spells affect many monsters that other magics cannot affect.  The type of resistance associated with these spells can also vary depending on the spell.
