\par \pard 
\par \fs20 Default combat takes place every 2 seconds.  And to make things more interesting, It also takes place in real time - whether you\'92re ready or not. Every round, you have the option of selecting what you wish to do.  You can fight, cast a spell, open a treasure container (if any), or just run.  The symbol in front of the monster group tells you which group you are currently fighting and what your selection was for that round.  To change the current monster group, hit either a number key for the new group (I.E. 1-4) or click on the monster.  You can only fight one monster group at a time.
