\par \fs20\cf1 AH:\cf2  \plain\fs20 Average hit points received when making a level before reaching the level of ML.\fs24 
\par \pard\li355\fi-355 \fs20\cf1 ML:\b  \plain\fs20 The Maximum level up to which AH hit points are received.  After reaching ML, MH hit points are received.\fs24 
\par \pard \fs20\cf1 MH:\b  \plain\fs20 Hit points received when making new levels after reaching ML.\fs24 
\par \pard\li355\fi-355 \fs20\cf1 EP:\b  \plain\fs20 Experience Parameter.  The higher the number, the more experience required to make a level.
\par \cf1 QP:\b  \plain\fs20 Quest Parameter.  The percentage chance that a character will be assigned a quest after making a level, requiring the quest to be completed before making the next level.\fs24 
\par \pard \fs20 
\par The Str, Int, etc. are the minimum stats required to enter the guild.  G, N, E, represents the alignments allowed in the guild.
\par 
