\pard\keepn \plain\b\fs28 Kill Spells\plain\fs24 
\par \pard 
\par \fs20 Created in a parallel study by the Mages and Wizards guilds as they crafted the Mind spells; the Kill spells, which revolved around direct mental and spiritual forms of attack, would either kill the victim outright or have absolutely no affect.  The effectiveness of these spells depends on the experience of the caster and the Magic Resistance of the target.
\par \fs24 
\par \pard\li175 \b\fs20 Nerve Blank\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 1\tab Guilds: Mag, Wiz
\par Required Stats: 11 Int, 7 Wis\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 2 Monsters in 2 Groups to be Killed.\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 This spell causes all nerves in the designated targets to stop functioning, causing death. Similar to the Paralyzing Death spell, but requires less ability to master.
\par 
\par \b Dazzle\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 3\tab Guilds: Mag, Wiz
\par Required Stats: 13 Int, 8 Wis, 8 Dex\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 6 Monsters in 4 Groups to be Dazzled.\tab 
\par \pard\li175 \plain\fs20 A more advanced form of Nerve Blank, this spell also affects the spirit as well, attempting to extinguish it.
\par 
\par \b Flickering Doom\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 5\tab Guilds: Mag, Wiz
\par Required Stats: 16 Int, 13 Wis, 12 Dex\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 7 Monsters in 4 Groups to be Killed.\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 When invoked, this spell paralyzes the victims with a blinding light then sucks their life force from their helpless bodies.
\par 
\par \b Cause Death\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 8\tab Guilds: Mag, Wiz
\par Required Stats: 18 Int, 16 Wis, 14 Con, 12 Dex\tab 
\par \pard\li175 \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 8 Monsters in 4 Groups to be Killed.\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 A simple spell which drives the spirit from the flesh and attempts to shut down the mind and body.
\par 
\par \b Piercing Darkness\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 10\tab Guilds: Mag, Wiz
\par Required Stats: 17 Int, 18 Wis, 10 Cha, 12 Dex\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 10 Monsters in 4 Groups to be Scared.\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 It is said that this spell invokes a dark form from the spiritual world which penetrates its victims and consumes their life force.
\par \pard\li175 
\par \b Field of Death\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 Base Level: 14\tab Guilds: Mag
\par Required Stats: 22 Int, 22 Wis, 18 Con, 21 Dex\tab 
\par \i COMBAT Spell, will cause 20 Monsters in 4 Groups to be Immolated.\tab 
\par \plain\fs20 A more powerful and flexible form of Cause Death, this spell attacks the spirit with such power that the body is enveloped in flames and turned to ash.\fs24 
